text: Nemaschema ochreovittatum is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1978.BioLib.cz - Nemaschema ochreovittatum. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1978
